text: Kim Doo-kwan (; born 10 April 1959) is a South Korean Democratic Party politician. He was the Governor of the South Gyeongsang Province from 2010 to 2012. He was a member of the Member of the National Assembly from 2016 until 2024. He was an unsuccessful candidate for President of South Korea in the 2025 snap presidential election. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean politicians
